Class GameConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.cl.intelligentgamedesigner.coregame.GameConstants

  • public class GameConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that contains many constants used in the game. This class should not contain any constants concerning scoring.
